pageContext.claim: “On Wednesday, you probably heard, a very young person with a great life ahead was stabbed viciously -- violently killed by an MS-13 gang member who entered our country recently through the southern border....I haven't heard about this young person that was killed yesterday -- 16 years old. Brutally murdered.”
pageContext.analysis: The 16-year old victim, who was stabbed by three suspected MS-13 gang members who attend Huntington High School on Long Island, was not seriously injured and has been released from the hospital, according to local news reports.
